room_title: Escape room "Zombie on a Chain" by GetOut Games in Salt Lake City
review: We did the 'Zombie on a Chain' Escape Room! It was so much fun! Loved the zombie!! ‍ Best. Escape Room. Ever! Lizzie, Sean & Kyra; you three made the experience amazing and fun!! Thanks so much!! ‍

room_title: Escape room "Zombie on a Chain" by GetOut Games in Salt Lake City
review: Lots of screams and running around in the Zombie room! Super fun and the story kicks in right away. This is my second escape room and I really enjoyed it.

room_title: Escape room "Zombie on a Chain" by GetOut Games in Salt Lake City
review: This was an awesome experience! We did the Zombie escape room and it was fantastic! It was really challenging and our aide Chase and Doctor X were both helpful and hectic! We managed to barely make it out by the skin of our teeth and it was a great time! I'll be recommending this to anyone!
